# Real (and real-shaped) patient-derived data from the Python pipeline.
# Public site policy is sample/synthetic-only -- these files are dev-time
# artifacts for wiring up the real-data view locally, never meant to be
# committed. Mirrors BDI_ventify-main's out_real/ (gitignored, no carve-out).
/public/data/patient_rollup.json
/public/data/cluster_breaths.json
/public/data/patient_tsne.json
/public/data/patient_metadata.json
/public/data/waveforms/
